# Meta-request decomposer

## When invoked

After classification is **meta-request**: business driver, roadmap realignment, new milestone/epic/story structure.

## Runbook

1. Derive **Product Spark** candidates (coarse), **Ingot** candidates (story-shaped), **Forge Spark** candidates (only when execution is clear).
2. Map to **existing** `docs/requirements/WBS.md` ID scheme; update `docs/ROADMAP.md`, `docs/requirements/INDEX.md`, `docs/requirements/TRACEABILITY.md`, milestone tree under `docs/requirements/milestones/`.
3. Search for overlaps; **one** canonicalization action per candidate (`canonicalization-policy.mdc`).
4. Do **not** write under `blueprints/`; all changes in **`docs/`** / **`forge/releases/`** as applicable.

